## Getting Started

1. Review and customize the generated configuration files
2. Start the AO daemon:
   ```bash
   ao daemon start
   ```
3. View available tasks:
   ```bash
   ao task list
   ```
4. Create a new task:
   ```bash
   ao task create "Your task description"
   ```

